{"tid":589787,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"郭文貴表態：絕不反習","createTime":"2018-03-12T05:48:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T11:58:52.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9fce2bacbc5cbc5d3666eb7413d03ddac9e585bd","tid":589787,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:48:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180312/large/1520825637_418f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180312%2Flarge%2F1520825637_418f.jpg&h=fc93c11e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共修憲取消國家主席任期制，引起各界人士公開批評。曾大爆內地政局醜聞的流亡中國富商郭文貴，日前透過影片痛斥，習近平政權在修憲後就要像電影《教父》一樣，開始對反對者進行滅口。但郭文貴態度反覆，他隔天又說反對修憲但不反對習近平。<br />\n<br />\n「這次修憲是光明正大盜國行徑，體現以黑治國，14億人民沉默，但這幾千人（人大代表）能代表人民嗎？」郭文貴上周五（9日）在其經營的「Guo Media郭媒體」上公佈一段影片，談論中共修憲企圖，他認為這次修憲，就是在位者想永遠執政擁有權力，而習近平打算終身執政，接下來還會清黨、滅口，「像電影《教父》裏面一樣，全部洗乾淨」。<br />\n<br />\n他悲觀地說：「這些人下一步就是要清黨、滅口、控制軍隊，中國政治大革命時代就要到來。」然而這個過程並非首次在中國發生，就像曾被稱為「毛澤東親密戰友」的林彪叛逃事件（913事件），郭文貴說「這種事情常有。」<br />\n<br />\n但這段影片發表後，郭文貴就在全國人大通過修憲前一天，又再錄製一段影片，改口說他反對修憲，卻絕不反對習近平，他還鄭重其事地連說3次：「郭文貴絕對不反習。不反習。不反習。不反習。」<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴又指，最近有不少人提供他許多「假訊息」，要他爆料習近平家人的腐敗，而他打算把這些資料全部蒐集起來，提供給習近平，讓他去找爆料者。郭文貴說，有心人士故意策動他反對習近平並爆料醜聞，就是要讓他成為中國的國家公敵，而他「絕不會上這個當」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180312/57935233\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180312%2F57935233&d=Jd8DbL3f2CtNCvN5tg%2Fm1RFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=0841ad00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180312%2F57935233&h=3cedd14b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180312/57935233</a>"},{"pid":"a80e8f7ebab1753399c50b8420d8ec7b6279ca54","tid":589787,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:50:28.000Z","msg":"而家先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n太遲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d69f31672dd5e482afde29374d784fe3808e163c","tid":589787,"uid":49392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:50:48.000Z","msg":"人在美國都要淆底，無撚用"},{"pid":"aa0f6c0a82370fd65b5bb1c790f16082d907f07c","tid":589787,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d69f31672dd5e482afde29374d784fe3808e163c","tid":589787,"uid":49392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:50:48.000Z","msg":"人在美國都要淆底，無撚用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:51:52.000Z","msg":"中國咁多spy 一陣死左都唔知咩事"},{"pid":"1adc055c5d4a73c0955b387cd440705920cbe586","tid":589787,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:52:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0fe7b84303ae0e97c4c3242a90351d594a981f8","tid":589787,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T06:00:16.000Z","msg":"重等緊你條片呀喂"},{"pid":"2bf26f258ee84332ea5bddb3819b96631f0a1ad3","tid":589787,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T06:01:57.000Z","msg":"范冰冰呢屌你老母"},{"pid":"eb2efc7508f8e09705ac951cbcd95633407cdaee","tid":589787,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T06:10:07.000Z","msg":"死鳩硬啦<br />\n<br />\n而家王歧山可能做中國第二把交椅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲以為唔反習就得"},{"pid":"f8e0d8359e78bf6ca5740120a8dc4c02d87b0819","tid":589787,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"